{"tid":1658642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[諮詢期最後一日] 一人一信保留通識科","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T14:41:07.000Z","uid":125861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6f54497987f698bc2fc256df11aa0507bfadbc","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzBp8Qn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzBp8Qn.jpg&h=8fab5566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEmail去: <br />\ntaskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\nTo whom it may concern,<br />\n<br />\nI am an ordinary Hong Kong citizen. I suggest keeping Liberal Studies as a core subject in secondary school. <br />\n<br />\nI strongly believe that, firstly, Liberal Studies helps student build up their own point of views. It cultivates students&rsquo; critical thinking skills and provide the future generation with wider knowledge base, independent thinking and creativity in a knowledge-oriented society. <br />\n<br />\nSecondly, it broadens students&rsquo; knowledge base. It also increases students&rsquo; learning incentive by providing an integration of knowledge of all subject mutually.<br />\n<br />\nThirdly, the subject also prevents students&rsquo; one-track approach due to specialisation in secondary subjects. <br />\n<br />\nThe main reason for establishing Liberal Studies as a major subject is to equip students with the critical thinking skill and care for political affairs in society. As it was first introduced by the Education Bureau, &ldquo;In a rapidly changing society, students need to be equipped with a broad base of knowledge, high adaptability, independent thinking skills and an ability to engage in life-long learning. Liberal Studies enables students to prepare themselves for various challenges in the future.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, I sincerely plead for keeping Liberal Studies as a core subject in secondary education. Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nBest Regards<br />\nXXX<br />\nA Hong Kong citizen"},{"pid":"8adf75feebedff2a35cd0ea38c3867334f5e5bbe","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e6bd1c1c9cfba5e4721b309e1c484e8fcf3dd09d","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"caf0511d20a6aac24f61b51401b28511611261cc","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"7b0c52e4410f04fc1d2de68e8afbef5f37dabf51","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7803f541ba7b491af52934630e62138c393741f3","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9f8051d8c576aa6c7029fdb6d55909abdb73f5fd","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"a2895d4aa4fd094430bb605db1478962352ea234","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:22.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"63421d5b611355cbda91c5e82a625a57e3ff61f5","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"d361430751818f4c97b1e28bbd1f9c0d98c6762e","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"5177ae2513815a8e5b427297064e3b16cf6c7599","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"d9881ee34f8a9d177f8c84fdeae05890320369c6","tid":1658642,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style